  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1752582150577",
    "pv": "1",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1259479258473041920",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年7月8日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年7月14日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年7月15日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：调整价格违规处置措施，增加处置项。</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">第二类价格违规修订内容如下：</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">商家发布商品价格违反法律法规、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0060ff; background: white;\">《</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090450620420329472&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0060ff; background: white;\">京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0060ff; background: white;\">个体商品管理规则</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #0060ff; background: white;\">》</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">等规则，违规情形包括但不限于</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #404040; background: white;\">价格虚高、提价促销、违背价格承诺、运费虚高、价格波动异常、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">宣传价格与实际不符</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #404040; background: white;\">、不当发布价格信息、价格引流、其他价格违规行为等</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #404040; background: white;\">京东有权依据法律法规、平台规则及协议等进行处理，并有权视违规程度采取包括</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">但不限于预警、下架违规商品、限制营销活动、限制广告活动、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">降低店铺星级、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">要求商家支付50元以上1000000元以下违约金、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">加收保证金、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">搜推屏蔽/降权、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">商品详情页屏蔽、限制区域销售、限制商品上架/发布、限制店铺发布商品数量、钱包冻结、类目/品牌停用、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺关停清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</div>",
